Holepunch|https://holepunch.recruitee.com|Senior Node.js Engineer|Full-time|Remote

Job requirements

- Significant experience with Node.js;

- Experience with C/C++ and writing native bindings for Node is a plus but not required;

- A strong background in building and managing modular codebases and creating reusable npm modules;

- Robust Testing & Debugging experience;

- Passion for P2P Technology is a plus.

Why Holepunch?

This is more than just a job; it’s an opportunity to be at the forefront of the internet’s evolution.

If you are driven by innovation and eager to build decentralized solutions that challenge the status quo, join Holepunch. Together, we can create a more secure, inclusive, and P2P decentralized future.
